   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The fifth year of the new era: April</h2>

<p> In the 5th year of the new age on April 1st, 'The Wolves of Moshran', lead by Lorck are attacked by the orc clan 'The Bloodskulls', More arguments follow. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 3rd April, an attempt to assassinate the orc Byron is carried out, leaving him badly wounded. The attack was carried out in broad daylight in front of several witnesses. Markous accuses Lorck of the attack. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 3rd April, Jonathan Glanwen, son of Gwynnether and John Glanwen is born. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 5th April, Lady Quinasa invites an open audience to Varshikar to discuss matters regarding the town. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 7th of April, the Orcish clan 'The Bloodskulls' declare that the city of Trollsbane is to now be called 'Skullsbane', this is soon discarded when met by protests from other citizens. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 9th of April, the Grey Rose holds a ceremony in celebration of its anniversary, many guests are invited. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 10th of April, an elven ceremony takes place to celebrate the completion of the Elven town 'Tol Vanima'. Only Elves are invited. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 13th of April, Callith, Fooser and Marius Eisenhauer are confronted by several drow outside The Falkner's Shrine. They are told to not cut the trees or harm any creature in the forest. The drow threaten to attack the town otherwise. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 17th of April, The kingdom of Silverbrand announces that all current contracts held are to be cancelled. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 23rd April, The Orc Wiergraf is banned from town permanently. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 24th April, a celebration in the House of the Druids of the Forest is held. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 24th April, the town guard Durin Goldtooth is accused of murder. This eventually leads to his resignation of the position. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 27th of April, Durin Goldtooth makes an announcement to the Dwarves of Silverbrand, to keep their smithing tools and secrets to themselves. It is met with disdain from other citizens. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 27th of April, Pendar Fayed announces that he has been appointed the Captain of the Town Guard. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 30th of April, The newly appointed Town Guard Captain Pendar Fayed releases a charter listing the rules and Constitution of Trollsbane. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 30th of April, Josephine pursues a thief named Wolfhelm, they are both attacked by a troll in the forest and Wolfhelm is wounded. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the 30th of April, The Dwarf Donder Lightsmith tries to prevent three Orcs, lead by Vay Gan, from entering the Grey Refuge, he fails and tries to call assistance from the citizens of Trollsbane. </p>


